HEADWORD: Conquian
<hw>Con"qui*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Card
Playing)</fld> <def>A game for two, played with 40 cards, in which each
player tries to form three or four of a kind or sequences.</def>⟦br⟧
